<Layout title="Installation - STEREO Internet Toolkit">
  <article style="margin-top: -1px;">
    <h2 id="intallation" class="mt0">Installation</h2>

    Requirements
    <ul>
      <li>php (minversion? 7.4?)</li>
      <li>composer</li>
      <!-- <li>mysql</li> -->
      <li>apache or nginx (for deployment, will run locally just fine w/ php's built-in server)</li>
    </ul>

    apache requires mod_rewrite to be enabled<br />
    idk php required extensions?<br /><br />


    good to have mysql, but not required.<br /><br />

    *** highly recommend dbngin & herd ***
    
    <br /><br />

    install slim & stuff
    <p>
      <code>composer create-project jyoungblood/stereo [new-project-name]</code>
    </p>
    <p><code>cd [new-project-name]; mv .env.example .env</code></p>
    <p><code>composer start</code></p>
    <p><code>php -S localhost:8080 -t public</code> also works</p>
    <p>you can use herd too</p>

    <br /><br />
    install tailwind & vite (optional)
    <p><code>npm install</code></p>
    <p><code>npm run dev</code></p>

